&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Bristol Eye Hospital is looking to recruit a full time Permeant Clinic Coordinator to working within the busy Outpatients Booking Team to assist with the Processing of GP e-RS referrals,. for the Ophthalmology Department.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to have good attention to detail and IT skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Any NHS or a healthcare environment experience would also be an advantage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Due to the very large responses we receive for jobs we are unable to respond to all candidates individually at application stage. Therefore, if you have not heard from us, you have regretfully been unsuccessful on this occasion.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Teresa Naish&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Assistant Performance &amp; Operations Manager (Non Admitted)&lt;/p&gt;
